{"id": "art-416", "label": "Art. 416", "title": "Art. 416: Formele recunoaşterii", "slug": "art-416", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 416: Formele recunoa&#351;terii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1509756620\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1150\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1509756620\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Recunoa&#351;terea poate fi f&#259;cut&#259; prin\ndeclara&#355;ie la serviciul public comunitar local de eviden&#355;&#259; a\npersoanelor, prin înscris autentic sau prin testament.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2133450134\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1149\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2133450134\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dac&#259; recunoa&#351;terea este f&#259;cut&#259; prin\nînscris autentic, o copie a acestuia este trimis&#259; din oficiu serviciului\npublic comunitar local de eviden&#355;&#259; a persoanelor competent, pentru a\nse face men&#355;iunea corespunz&#259;toare în registrele de stare civil&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Recunoa&#351;terea, chiar\ndac&#259; a fost f&#259;cut&#259; prin testament, este irevocabil&#259;.</span></p>"}